Do you want to visit the Amazon Rainforest to see the piranhas? Do you want to go to the rainforests in Yunnan to find Asian elephants and gibbons? Or, do you want to walk in the tropical rainforests in Hainan and learn survival skills? Maybe you may want to travel around countries with rich rainforests in Southeast Asia? On June 22, CGTN takes you on a tour of the world's most enchanting rainforests! Let's start our journey! (Cover image designed by Yu Peng, video edited by Xing Fangyu) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)